Text:
Thanks for this, been looking forward to it since it was announced to get a UK release. At 75% currently but not many seeders compared to leechers so its going a tad slow now.

I will be seeding this for as awhile.

@MasterCain I'm with you on this one mate, games like these very rarely get a release outside of japan. If we want more games like the superb Xenoblade, Last Story and this we need to go out and buy them to show support to the developers to show them there is a market for games like these to release to in the future.
